---

## ⚠️ Common Beginner Mistakes

❌ Generating only once
❌ Not listening carefully
❌ Changing too many things at once

---

## 💡 Pro Tips

### 1. Keep Notes

Write:

* Prompt used
* What you liked
* What you didn’t

---

### 2. Change One Thing at a Time

👉 Helps you learn faster

---

### 3. Trust Your Ears

👉 You don’t need music theory
👉 Just listen and feel

---

